🚀 BayirExpress RAG Chatbot

BayirExpress RAG is an intelligent Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot built to help users quickly find and interact with transport announcements .

It combines:

FastAPI → backend API with retrieval + LLM integration.

CSV Data Pipeline → announcements data as the knowledge base.

Streamlit → modern and interactive chat interface.

Docker & Docker Compose → easy deployment.

📂 Project Structure
bayirExpress_chatbot/
│
├── RAG/
│   ├── app.py               # FastAPI backend
│   ├── utils.py             # RAG utilities (embeddings, search, etc.)
│   ├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
│   └── data/
│       └── annonces.csv     # Dataset of transport announcements
│
├── streamlit_app.py         # Streamlit chat interface
├── Dockerfile               # Dockerfile for FastAPI
├── docker-compose.yml       # Compose setup for API + (optionally UI)
└── README.md                # This file


🎨 Features

🔍 RAG-based retrieval → answers grounded in annonces.csv

📊 Transport announcement search → departure, arrival, price/kg, etc.

💬 Chat interface → Streamlit UI for easy interaction

🐳 Dockerized backend → portable and easy to deploy

⚡ FastAPI API → JSON responses for chatbot integration

🛠️ Tech Stack

FastAPI

Streamlit

LangChain
 (for RAG pipeline)

